title: 11.5: Sports Romance - Interstitial
dc:creator: Jennifer Prokop
description: Are you a sports ball fan?! Do we have romances for you! We’ve got the brilliant Jenny Nordbak from The Wicked Wallflowers podcast back for a sports romance interstitial! Listen to us chat about why we love sports books, the alpha, competence porn and books by Kennedy Ryan, Tamsen Parker, and Naima Simone!
itunes:author: Fated Mates
itunes:subtitle: Jen, Sarah, and Jenny Nordbak talk sports romance.
